[Electrasonic](http://web.archive.org/web/20150302020007/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/device/electrasonic/) is not as extreme, but it is angular.

- Mike Yanega

Another suggestion is Chank's [Brimley](http://web.archive.org/web/20150302020007/http:/new.myfonts.com/fonts/chank/brimley/), also not as extreme, but certainly angular.

- Mike Yanega

Thanks Mike,

Looking for something slightly more angular.

Cheers  
R
